CalculatedInsightRangeBound.name: CalculatedInsightRangeBound
CalculatedInsightRangeBound.description: Stores the information required to calculate a range-bound data insight.

LastReferencedDate.description: The timestamp when the current user last accessed this record, a record related to this record, or a list view.

LastViewedDate.description: The timestamp when the current user last viewed this record or list view. If this value is null, the user might have only accessed this record or list view (LastReferencedDate) but not viewed it.

LowerBoundRange.description: The lower limit of the calculated insight.

Name.description: The autogenerated name of the insight.

Operator.description: Operation used to calculate the insight based on the upper bound range and lower bound range.

OwnerId.description: ID of the contact who owns the insight.

SalesStoreId.description: The ID of the webstore associated with the insight benchmarks.

UpperBoundRange.description: The upper limit of the calculated insight.
